snippet.title: 『Seduce Me』Chained the Monster (TV-Sized) - Official Opening & Trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY THE DEMO HERE VVV
http://www.mediafire.com/download/7wwh15x72p86cdj/SeduceMeDemo-1.0-all.zip

This is an upcoming free-to-play otome game, produced by Seraphim Entertainment and Michaela Laws. Like what you see? Download the FULL GAME this Valentines Day!

-----

Shhhhh this is a new and final edit of the Seduce Me OP video...

Hiya lovelies! So, this is the final version of our trailer video for Seduce Me the Otome! -heart- It features the lovely talent of Seduce Me's new artists, Camille Ruley and Badriel and features our game's main theme song, Chained the Monster! Purchase the full song on Bandcamp now!

http://riseofthephoenix.bandcamp.com/releases

We truly hope you enjoy it and try out the updated official demo above! If you're as excited about this game as I am, make sure to plan ahead and download the full game on Valentines Day!!

Credits:

"Chained The Monster" - Seduce Me Opening Theme
Composed by Christopher Escalante
Lyrics by Michaela Laws
Vocals: Ability Pheonix
Guitar: Michael Kelly

----
